M a t e r i a l e x a m i n e d. Plishka Mt., 
<date id="1909101113005C5EFDB2F9F0CFB7F936" box="[580,674,1645,1667]" pageId="4" pageNumber="457" value="2018-05-06">6.05.2018</date>
